      • createCompactorListener

        Optional<CompactorListener> createCompactorListener(Properties properties)
                                             throws CompactorListenerCreationException
        Creates a CompactorListener, if none are specified returns Optional.absent().
        Parameters:
        properties - a Properties object used to create a CompactorListener.
        Returns:
        Optional.absent() if no CompactorListener is present, else returns a CompactorListener.
